#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:221
#, no-c-format
msgid "How to get more information"
msgstr "अधिकानि सूचनानि कथं प्राप्तव्यानि"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:224
#, no-c-format
msgid "Other &calligra; manuals"
msgstr "अन्ये &calligra; पुस्तिकाएँ"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:226
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"For detailed information on the different &calligra; applications, please "
"consult their respective manuals."
msgstr ""
"विभिन्नानां विषये विस्तृतसूचनार्थं &calligra; अनुप्रयोगेषु, कृपया तेषां स्वस्वपुस्तिकानां परामर्शं "
"कुर्वन्तु।"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:237
#, no-c-format
msgid "Links"
msgstr "लिङ्कानि"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:239
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The following links should be useful if you're looking for more information "
"about &kde; or &calligra;."
msgstr "यदि भवान् &kde; अथवा &calligra;."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:246
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<ulink url=\"http://calligra.org\">The &calligra; homepage</ulink>. Here you "
"can find information on how to get and install &calligra;, news about "
"&calligra; development, screenshots &etc;"
msgstr ""
"<ulink url=\"http://calligra.org\">कलिग्रा; मुखपृष्ठम्</ulink>। अत्र भवन्तः "
"&calligra;, &calligra; विकासः, स्क्रीनशॉट् इत्यादयः;"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:251
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<ulink url=\"http://www.kde.org\">The &kde; Homepage</ulink>. &kde; is the "
"most advanced and absolutely free desktop environment for unix-like "
"operating systems. &calligra; makes use of the &kde; libraries."
msgstr ""
"<ulink url=\"http://www.kde.org\">कडे; मुखपृष्ठम्</ulink>। &kde; यूनिक्स-सदृशानां "
"प्रचालनतन्त्राणां कृते सर्वाधिकं उन्नतं सर्वथा मुक्तं च डेस्कटॉप् वातावरणम् अस्ति । &calligra; "
"&kde इत्यस्य उपयोगं करोति; पुस्तकालयाः।"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:257
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<ulink url=\"http://qt-project.org/\">&Qt; page</ulink>. The creators of the "
"C++-toolkit &Qt;. &kde; and &calligra; make use of &Qt;."
msgstr ""
"<ulink url=\"http://qt-project.org/\">&Qt; पृष्ठ</ulink> इति । C++-toolkit "
"&Qt; इत्यस्य निर्मातारः । &kde; तथा &calligra; &Qt; इत्यस्य उपयोगं कुर्वन्तु।"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:267
#, no-c-format
msgid "Programming &calligra;"
msgstr "प्रोग्रामिंग &calligra;"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:271
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you want to do &calligra; development, the following resources might be "
"of interest:"
msgstr "यदि भवान् कर्तुम् इच्छति &calligra; विकासे निम्नलिखितसंसाधनाः रुचिकराः भवेयुः।"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:277
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"At <ulink url=\"http://techbase.kde.org/Development\">http://techbase.kde."
"org/Development</ulink> you'll find many documents about programming with "
"&Qt; and &kde;. You can find the online version of the complete &kde; "
"library documentation on <ulink url=\"http://api.kde.org/\">KDE API "
"Reference</ulink>"
msgstr ""
"<ulink url=\"http://techbase.kde.org/Development\">http://techbase.kde.org/"
"Development</ulink> इत्यत्र भवन्तः &Qt; तथा &kde;. सम्पूर्णस्य &kde; <ulink url="
"\"http://api.kde.org/\">KDE API सन्दर्भ</ulink> इत्यत्र पुस्तकालयस्य दस्तावेजीकरणं"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:283
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The first step for contributing code is to follow <ulink url=\"http://"
"community.kde.org/Calligra/Building/Building_Calligra\">those instructions</"
"ulink> to get the source code and build it."
msgstr ""
"कोडं योगदानं दातुं प्रथमं सोपानं स्रोतसङ्केतं प्राप्तुं तस्य निर्माणार्थं च <ulink url=\"http://"
"community.kde.org/Calligra/Building/Building_Calligra\">तानि निर्देशानि</"
"ulink> अनुसरणं करणीयम् ।"

